35:15.880 --> 35:17.575
To your knowledge,
Mrs. Florrick,

35:17.610 --> 35:20.204
has Lemond Bishop contributed
money to your campaign

35:20.250 --> 35:22.218
or PACs supporting
your campaign?

35:22.250 --> 35:23.877
Yes.

35:25.350 --> 35:27.318
Yes, he did?

35:27.350 --> 35:30.285
The top drug dealer in town did?

35:30.320 --> 35:33.289
Yes, I had no control
of what he did.

35:33.330 --> 35:36.322
Bishop told me
that he was financing my PAC.

35:38.770 --> 35:41.739
We're very impressed,
Mrs. Florrick.

35:41.770 --> 35:44.432
We're used to th_e_c_anned answers
of politICIans,

35:44.470 --> 35:46.904
the casual lies,

35:46.940 --> 35:50.171
but you've been very brave in
here today by telling the truth.

35:50.210 --> 35:53.179
So we're gonna give
you our endorsement.

35:53.210 --> 35:54.472
Really?

35:54.520 --> 35:56.613
GRACE: That was
very brave of you, Mom.

35:56.650 --> 35:58.641
One doesn't need God
to act ethically.

36:01.890 --> 36:03.858
ELI:
